#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.14"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.14:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.14:0.2"
msgid "2. Dhammacakkappavattanavagga "
msgstr "2. Rolling Forth the Wheel of Dhamma "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 14. Ajjhattikāyatanasutta → āyatanasuttaṃ (bj) | āyatana (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.14:0.3"
msgid "14. Ajjhattikāyatanasutta "
msgstr "14. Interior Sense Fields "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn56.14:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, ariyasaccāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these four noble truths. "

msgctxt "sn56.14:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn56.14:1.3"
msgid "Dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ. "
msgstr "The noble truths of suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.14:2.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ? "
msgstr "And what is the noble truth of suffering? "

msgctxt "sn56.14:2.2"
msgid "‘Cha ajjhattikāni āyatanānī’tissa vacanīyaṃ. "
msgstr "You should say: ‘The six interior sense fields’. "

msgctxt "sn56.14:2.3"
msgid "Katamāni cha? "
msgstr "What six? "

msgctxt "sn56.14:2.4"
msgid "Cakkhāyatanaṃ … pe … manāyatanaṃ—"
msgstr "The sense fields of the eye, ear, nose, tongue, body, and mind. "

msgctxt "sn56.14:2.5"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ. "
msgstr "This is called the noble truth of suffering. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.14:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.14:3.2"
msgid "Yāyaṃ taṇhā ponobbhavikā nandirāgasahagatā tatratatrābhinandinī, seyyathidaṃ—kāmataṇhā, bhavataṇhā, vibhavataṇhā—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.14:3.3"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhasamudayaṃ ariyasaccaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn56.14:4.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.14:4.2"
msgid "Yo tassāyeva taṇhāya asesavirāganirodho cāgo paṭinissaggo mutti anālayo—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.14:4.3"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhaṃ ariyasaccaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn56.14:5.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.14:5.2"
msgid "Ayameva ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.14:5.3"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.14:5.4"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā ariyasaccaṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn56.14:5.5"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri ariyasaccāni. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn56.14:6.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.14:6.2"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
